# PDF Controllers

Reserved for HTTP controllers that expose PDF-related REST endpoints in the future.

Currently, PDF generation is triggered internally via:
- `PdfRequestHandler` (WhatsApp interactive button reply)
- `WhatsAppNotificationService.sendInvoicePdf()` (orchestrator)

If a REST endpoint for PDF download is needed (e.g. `GET /api/invoices/:id/pdf`),
add the controller here and register it in `PdfModule`.
